/keld
*.test
# Local installer dry-run build output dirs (installers-<os>-<arch>/, e.g. from
# `act`/local CI runs) and the Inno Setup output dir — not the tracked installers/
# source tree itself. An earlier bare `/installers*` pattern here accidentally
# matched that tracked dir too (no untracked files under it could be `git add`ed).
/installers-*/
/installers/windows/Output/

# GoReleaser build output
/dist/

# Python bytecode
__pycache__/
*.pyc
